<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Why COVID-19 Could Trigger a Surprise Billing Crisis</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="801" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1200x801.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A woman holds her head and looks at bills" itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-800x534.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-2048x1367.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills.jpg 2119w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="801" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A woman holds her head and looks at bills" itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1200x801.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-400x267.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-200x133.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-800x534.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-2048x1367.jpg 2048w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills.jpg 2119w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0327-billsbillsbills-1200x801.jpg" loading="lazy">
<figcaption class="wp-caption-text" itemprop="caption">Third-party companies that bill for out-of-network care stand to profit from the pandemic, at the expense of the ill.</figcaption><figcaption class="wp-caption-credit" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Juanmonino / Getty Images</span></figcaption></figure></div>
