<article class="row hentry post-269464 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-coronavirus tag-covid-19 tag-emergency-room tag-health-care tag-health-insurance tag-medical-bills tag-surprise-bills section-environment-and-health primary_topic-health" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/us-is-not-prepared-for-coronavirus-we-need-a-massive-expansion-of-health-care/" title="US Is Not Prepared for Coronavirus. We Need a Massive Expansion of Health Care.">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="A person wears a face mask as a precaution while shopping in New York, March 2, 2020. New York confirmed its first case of the novel coronavirus late Sunday." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_0303-coronavirus-us-2400x1800.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='categories'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/category/op-ed/' rel='category' class='op-ed'>Op-Ed</a>
</div>
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/us-is-not-prepared-for-coronavirus-we-need-a-massive-expansion-of-health-care/">US Is Not Prepared for Coronavirus. We Need a Massive Expansion of Health Care.</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Without competent leadership and a universal health care system, it is up to us to take action in our communities.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/kevin-zeese/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Kevin Zeese</a></span> & </dd>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/margaret-flowers/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Margaret Flowers</a></span>, </dd>
